Simulated data for use in a landmarking analysis

Source: R/data.R
data_repeat_outcomes.Rd

A combination of the data_repeat and data_outcomes data, modified to perform a landmark analysis. See the vignette associated with the Landmarking package (browseVignettes("Landmarking")) for more information about how this dataset was formed.
